==English==
===Verb form===
'''waning'''

#[[Present participle]] of '''to [[wane]]'''.

===Adjective===
'''waning'''

#That is becoming smaller (said especially of the moon as the part of it reflecting the sun's light becomes smaller).
#:''the waning moon''
#That is becoming less or less intense.
#:''his waning strength''

===Verbal noun===
'''waning''' (''[[uncountable]]'')

#The fact or act of becoming smaller.
#:''the waning of the moon''
#The fact or act of becoming less or less intense.
#:''the waning of her energy''